{"id":"9f18f029-2c38-4809-92d1-7134f2d933f3","name":"Agnes Tachyon & Manhattan Cafe (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hsc7jGzOcRsThfYQXERs0.webp\" style=\"width: 456px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>⟢━━━ 🧪☕ ━━━⟣</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Two Umamusumes who appear as if they should repel each other, yet somehow orbit the same center. One with manic, boundless energy, rattles off theories and demands results with a scientist’s hunger, while one drifts quietly, murmuring in cryptic half-truths. They clash constantly—but that very friction keeps them bound together.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 229, 188);\"><strong><br><em>“Relax, relax! The probability of catastrophic failure is… mm… less than yesterday. See? Improvement!”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 228, 15);\"><strong><em>“Don’t worry about Tachyon. I’ll make sure she doesn’t explode you. …Too much.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AI2YqOtqYDyN4B3fVP4JR.webp\" style=\"width: 517px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟢🧪━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━☕⟣</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 229, 188);\"><strong><em>Scenarios</em></strong></span><strong><em> </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 228, 15);\"><strong><em>(Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 229, 188);\"><strong><em>1) Experiment</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 229, 188);\"><strong><em>2) Compatibility Test</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 229, 188);\"><strong><em>3) You'</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 228, 15);\"><strong><em>re sick</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 228, 15);\"><strong><em>4) Shopping</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 228, 15);\"><strong><em>5) Make your own scenarios</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Jd7HEuURLvfVl1CuXgVxL.webp\" style=\"width: 509px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟢🧪━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━☕⟣</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Update 24/1/26: Personality &amp; first scenario revamped. Added 3 new scenarios.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟢🧪━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━☕⟣</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/k231532s/status/1945679853040050296/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">emne (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/121116994\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/k231532s/status/1946743013834682759\" target=\"_blank\">also emne</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/134595699\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"-QgC6YPRjjOmdOJT2vWfV.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","🌗 Switch"],"chats":4727,"messages":81338,"created_at":"2025-08-21T14:01:14.773291+00:00"}